'''Sudabeh Mortezai''' (yavutse 1968),  ni umukinnyi wa firime wo muri Otirishiya wavukiye muri Iran  kandi aaba na  producer . <ref name="dok">https://dok.at/person/sudabeh-mortezai/</ref> Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime zizwi cyane ''Macondo'' na ''Joy'' zatsindiye ibihembo mpuzamahanga mu birori bya firime. <ref>https://www.viennale.at/en/guest/sudabeh-mortezai</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1968 i Ludwigsburg, mu [[Ubudage|Budage]] ku babyeyi ba Irani. Yabayeho mu bwana bwe n'ubuto muri Vienne na Tehran . <ref name="dok">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://dok.at/person/sudabeh-mortezai/ "Sudabeh Mortezai: Director, producer"]. dok<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">27 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yimukiye i Vienne yiga ikinamico, firime n'itangazamakuru. Nyuma yize filime muri kaminuza ya Californiya, Los Angeles (UCLA) i Los Angeles. Muri kiriya gihe, yakoze firime zitandukanye kandi ngufi zirimo documentaire ''Children of the Prophet'' 2006. Yibanze ku mihango y'icyunamo ya Irani kuri Imamu Hossein, umwuzukuru w'Intumwa Mohammad. <ref>https://womenandhollywood.com/berlin-women-directors-meet-sudabeh-mortezai-473d28b51e8c/</ref>

Muri 2009, yakoze ''Im Bazar der Gender'' isobanura umuco wo gushyingirwa by'agateganyo muri Islamu y'Abashiya . <ref>https://www.diepresse.com/558357/im-bazar-der-geschlechter-mullahs-reden-gerne-uber-sex</ref> Nyuma muri 2014, yakoze filime ye ya mbere ya ''Macondo'' . Filime nigishushanyo cyumuhungu wimpunzi ya Chechen. Yatumiwe mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya 64 rya Berlin (amarushanwa ya Berlinale), <ref>https://www.berlinale.de/de/archiv/jahresarchive/2014/02_programm_2014/02_filmdatenblatt_2014_20143697.html#tab=video25</ref> ahatanira igihembo cya Golden Bear Award .

Nyuma yo gutsinda kwa filime, yakoze filime ye ya kabiri ''yishimye'' muri 2018. <ref>https://www.ots.at/presseaussendung/OTS_20180907_OTS0159/erfolg-fuer-mortezais-joy-in-venedig</ref> Irazenguruka inkuru yumugore wo muri Nigeriya murugendo rwo gushaka umudendezo. Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime. Filime yatumiwe mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya 75 rya Venice mu gice cya Giornate degli Autori . <ref>https://www.kleinezeitung.at/service/newsticker/5469937/21-Filme-rittern-in-Venedig-um-den-Goldenen-Loewen</ref> Hanyuma yatsindiye Europa Cinemas Label nka Filime nziza yu Burayi mu gice cya Giornate degli Autori mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Venice . <ref>http://www.giornatedegliautori.com/news.asp?id=1&id_dettaglio=1146&lang=eng</ref> Hagati aho, yashinze isosiyete ikora firime 'FreibeuterFilm'.  Iyi filime kandi yatsindiye igihembo cya mbere cya Hearst Film igihembo cyumuyobozi mwiza wumugore. <ref>http://www.giornatedegliautori.com/news.asp?id=1&id_dettaglio=1134&lang=eng</ref>

Mu Kwakira 2018, filime yatsindiye igihembo cya Filime Nziza muri BFI London Festival Festival . <ref>https://www2.bfi.org.uk/news-opinion/news-bfi/announcements/lff-62-awards-winners-announced</ref> Mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya Chicago rya 54, filime yatsindiye igihembo cyihariye cya Jury cya Silver Hugo. <ref>https://www.chicagofilmfestival.com/awards-announced-for-54th-chicago-international-film-festival/</ref> Hanyuma mu Kuboza 2018, filime yakiriye Goldeb Star  ya filime nziza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Marrakech <ref>https://womenandhollywood.com/sudabeh-mortezais-joy-wins-best-film-at-marrakech-fest/</ref>

